FBIS4-13072 "drnes074dd_94013" FBIS-NES-94-074 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 Palestinian Affairs Collaborators Receive Israeli Identity Cards Collaborators Receive Israeli Identity Cards TA1804072794 Jerusalem AL-NAHAR in Arabic 14 Apr 94 p 3 TA1804072794 Jerusalem AL-NAHAR Arabic BFN [Excerpt] In recent weeks, scores of collaborators with Israel have received blue Israeli identity cards. This came after the PLO, in its negotiations with Israel, refused to issue a general amnesty for collaborators. This identity card permits collaborators and their families to live wherever they wish in Israel. A large number of collaborators have expressed their intention to reside in Arab villages within the Green Line. [passage omitted]
